OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of Carl Holland in Belfast
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith the manslaughter of a man who
OL,8,Fdied following an incident outside a
OL,9,Fpub in west Belfast last month.
OL,11,FCarl Holland, 30, died in hospital
OL,12,Ffollowing the incident on June 12.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday morning Anthony Rooney,
OL,15,F20, of Gardenmore Way in Dunmurry,
OL,16,Fappeared before Belfast Magistrates'
OL,17,FCourt.
OL,19,FHe was told he is charged with
OL,20,Funlawfully killing Mr Holland contrary
OL,21,Fto common law.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
