PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784247521
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of Carl Holland in Belfast
OL,6,FHe replied "yeah" when asked if he
OL,7,Funderstood the charge.
OL,9,FA detective sergeant told the court
OL,10,Fshe believed she could connect the
OL,11,Faccused to the charge.
OL,13,FThe court heard that bail conditions
OL,14,Finclude residing at an address given
OL,15,Fin court which is outside Belfast, not
OL,16,Fto enter west Belfast apart from
OL,17,Ftransit on the M1 and no contact with
OL,18,Fwitnesses in the case.
OL,20,FThe next hearing of the case was set
OL,21,Ffor August 26.
